# Privacy Policy for NeoPaste

**Effective Date:** 11-01-2025

NeoPaste is committed to protecting your privacy. This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, and safeguard your data when you use our macOS app. By using NeoPaste, you agree to the terms outlined below.

---

## 1. Data Collection
NeoPaste does not collect, store, or share any personal information or data from your clipboard. All clipboard content is processed locally on your device and is not transmitted to any servers.

---

## 2. Use of Data
- Clipboard content is temporarily accessed locally for functionality purposes, such as formatting.  
- NeoPaste does not store or transmit clipboard data beyond the duration of the app's operation.

---

## 3. Third-Party Services
NeoPaste does not integrate or use any third-party services that collect user data.

---

## 4. Security
Since NeoPaste processes data entirely on your local device, no data is exposed to external networks, ensuring the highest level of security for your clipboard content.

---

## 5. Children's Privacy
NeoPaste is not intended for use by individuals under the age of 13. We do not knowingly collect any information from children.

---

## 6. Changes to This Policy
We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time to reflect improvements or changes to the app. You will be notified of any significant changes through our app or website.

---

## 7. Contact Us
If you have questions or concerns about this Privacy Policy, please contact us at:

